[{"title":"万事开头难","url":"https://mozfc.github.io/2017/07/20/page_1/","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/css/DPlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js\"> </script><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\"> </script><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;烈日炎炎似火烧，七月真的很长！<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;村子里又停电了，城市的夜晚并没有抵消一丁点儿白天积攒的热量，整个屋子里俨然就是一澡堂子里的桑拿房，让人喘不过气来，这个夏天冲凉水澡已是常态，非常态的是今晚两小时内已是第四次了冲洗了，此刻已用光了所有积攒的水资源，楼下吃火锅划拳的人还不少，发电机的噪音也没完没了的，此刻虽困如狗，但也毫无睡意。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;今天是有成就感的一天，两年来所积累的知识终于为自己服务了一把，经过两天两夜的研究实践，我的博客终于有了自己的生日。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;本来打算周天好好的做个博客释义，开个好头，怎奈天不遂愿，看来是熬不到周日了。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;古话说的对，好记性不如烂笔头，两年来感同身受，虽然零零总总的学会了很多东西，但所刻在脑子或者留在指尖的总是不能如愿，人总是后知后觉，现在才幡然领悟，原来是高估了自己的记忆力，痛定思痛，这才建立了自己的博客，以后凡一次不能深刻记忆的东西必将录入博客以便后观。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;曾经看到有技术大牛深发感慨，自己的进步和坚持写博客有很大的必然联系，前辈之鉴，后辈自学之，做此博客一是记录生活的所思所想，二是记录每个时间点所学会的技术知识，增加跨时记忆。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;已是凌晨一点半，燥热并没消减半分，猛地回头，半桶纯净水凸显眼前。。。<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;万事开头难，不忘初心，继续前行。。。</p>\n","categories":["生活感悟"],"tags":["所思所想"]},{"title":"Hello World","url":"https://mozfc.github.io/2016/06/01/hello-world/","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/css/DPlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js\"> </script><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\"> </script><p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ hexo server</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">Deployment</a></p>\n<div id=\"dplayer0\" class=\"dplayer\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\"></div><script>var dplayer0 = new DPlayer({\"element\":document.getElementById(\"dplayer0\"),\"autoplay\":false,\"theme\":\"#FADFA3\",\"loop\":true,\"video\":{\"url\":\"http://devtest.qiniudn.com/若能绽放光芒.mp4\",\"pic\":\"http://devtest.qiniudn.com/若能绽放光芒.png\"}});</script>\n<div id=\"aplayer0\" class=\"aplayer\" style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;\"></div>\n\t\t<script>\n\t\t\tnew APlayer({\n\t\t\t\telement: document.getElementById(\"aplayer0\"),\n\t\t\t\tnarrow: false,\n\t\t\t\tautoplay: false,\n\t\t\t\tshowlrc: 0,\n\t\t\t\tmusic: {\n\t\t\t\t\ttitle: \"停格\",\n\t\t\t\t\tauthor: \"蔡健雅\",\n\t\t\t\t\turl: \"/video/tingGe.mp3\",\n\t\t\t\t\tpic: \"/images/avatar.jpg\",\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t});\n\t\t</script>\n","categories":["Hexo教程"],"tags":["js"]},{"title":"project","url":"https://mozfc.github.io/project/index.html","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/css/DPlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js\"> </script><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\"> </script>","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"category","url":"https://mozfc.github.io/category/index.html","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/css/DPlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js\"> </script><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\"> </script>","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"link","url":"https://mozfc.github.io/link/index.html","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/css/DPlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js\"> </script><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\"> </script>","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"search","url":"https://mozfc.github.io/search/index.html","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/css/DPlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js\"> </script><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\"> </script>","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"about","url":"https://mozfc.github.io/about/index.html","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/css/DPlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js\"> </script><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\"> </script>","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"tag","url":"https://mozfc.github.io/tag/index.html","content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/assets/css/DPlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/DPlayer.min.js\"> </script><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\"> </script>","categories":[],"tags":[]}]